Blue Team (Defenders)

Process: Monitor retransmission rates and analyze abnormal packet ordering during incident investigations.

End Goal: Identify network attacks, infrastructure issues, or stealthy malware communications.

Red Team (Attackers)

Process: Exploit differences in packet reassembly between operating systems and intrusion detection systems to bypass detection.
End Goal: Deliver malicious traffic that security appliances fail to reconstruct correctly.
